Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:50.83,Main03,KONDO (M),0,0,0,,But to these guys, you're also an\Nirreplaceable part of that soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:55.84,Main03,KONDO (M),0,0,0,,Good to have you back...Toshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.79,0:20:57.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よく帰ってきてくれたな ﾄｼ》
